<a name="skipmaincontent"></a><h1 class="bac">Global Technology and Operations</h1>

<h2 class="bac">Overview</h2>

<p class="bac">In Asia, Operations ensures that all transactions are properly recorded, settled, billed and accounted for, irrespective of where the deals originate.  This calls for operations associates to focus on quality of input and productivity of throughput, while being vigilant for potential errors cause either from the client&acute;s submission or from another associate&acute;s initial capture.  Six sigma methodologies have been embraced as a culture to ensure highest standards of quality, productivity and performance measurement. Additionally transaction processing is conducted within a tightly controlled environment, both in terms of accounting standards and regulatory guidelines which vary from country to country in the region.</p>
<p class="bac">To attain this level of competency, we invest heavily in associate development, both “on the job” and in the classroom, and reward our associates through our Spirit Program for exceptional performance.  </p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" class="bac" alt=""><br clear="all">

<h2 class="bac">Qualifications</h2>
<p class="bac">Candidates must have obtained or are realistically expecting to obtain an MBA degree from a premier business school.  Candidate should have deep and broad finance knowledge, excellent verbal and written communication skills, and strong personal leadership skills.  </p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" class="bac" alt=""><br clear="all">

<h2 class="bac">Training</h2>
<p class="bac">Associates will participate in an orientation program and formal learning curriculum to learn more about the bank&acute;s business, culture and values.  Throughout the program, you&acute;ll have ample opportunities to work closely with professionals and peers throughout our organization. This is a great opportunity to build a network of colleagues from across the company that will prove to be a tremendous resource to you throughout your career.</p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" class="bac" alt=""><br clear="all">

<h2 class="bac">Placement</h2>
<p class="bac">Associates work in Mumbai, New Delhi, Chennai, Bangalore or Kolkata, India.  Offers are made for a specific product desk, based on candidate preference and business need.  Throughout the recruiting and orientation process, candidates have the opportunities to learn about various desks and meet team members and colleagues from across the company.</p>


<img src="../images/clear.gif" class="bac" alt=""><br clear="all">

